SPICABLE BEHAVIOR.</p>\n<p>No, Cassidy, Cornyn, Thune, or whomever is next, you are not ENTITLED to your position.</p>\n<p>The fact of the matter is you are losing due to your performance, not due to anything that DJT has done.</p>\n<p>YOU ARE NOT REPRESENTING THE WISHES OF YOUR STATE!</p>\n<p>It really is that simple.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 14, "score_up": 115, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}], "status": true}